synopsis: After getting into a paragliding accident, South Korean heiress Yun Se Ri crash lands in North Korea. There, she meets North Korean army officer Ri Jeong Hyeok, who agrees to help her return to South Korea. Despite the tension between their countries, the two of them start falling for one another.
